{"tid":1133344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工！】80後 疑曠工　同事登門揭發倒斃灣仔寓所","createTime":"2019-05-01T03:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T05:29:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":129,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"7fba0694aedd489212680e4c185cd3abf73245e7","tid":1133344,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"昨日(4月30日)傍晚6時許，警方接獲一名24歲姓鄭男子報案，指其一名31歲姓呂男同事，懷疑在灣仔春園街6至12號寓所單位內暈倒。救援人員趕到現場破門入屋，發現該名男事主倒斃屋內，當場證實死亡。據知事主疑因沒有上班，同事遂登門尋找，卻揭發事主已不治。警方經初步調查，相信事件沒有可疑，事主死因有待驗屍後確定，案件列作「屍體發現」跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/323903/31歲男子疑曠工-同事登門揭發倒斃灣仔寓所\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F323903%2F31%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%96%91%E6%9B%A0%E5%B7%A5-%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BB%E9%96%80%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E5%80%92%E6%96%83%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=1a464113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/323903/31歲男子疑曠工-同事登門揭發倒斃灣仔寓所</a>"},{"pid":"7c7ed0fb25454f5e37930b10764761eedfc3ff4f","tid":1133344,"uid":124277,"like":518,"dislike":4,"score":514,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"咁佢跟開d 野邊個跟"},{"pid":"a1f8e35d61b01d58e83a46d4d1cabded4554de96","tid":1133344,"uid":19454,"like":953,"dislike":8,"score":945,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"因沒有上班，同事遂登門尋找<br />\n因沒有上班，同事遂登門尋找<br />\n因沒有上班，同事遂登門尋找<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要捉人返工，not 出於care ，試下離左職，化左灰都冇人搵你"},{"pid":"69e09ab4dcf7e7809778a3ff1cb8399ae39e3702","tid":1133344,"uid":42188,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"凶宅 +1"},{"pid":"fa09cb8028565337d2675f7c0f0d51b75cf0a185","tid":1133344,"uid":186152,"like":147,"dislike":1,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"因為曠工先被發現"},{"pid":"8100ff57e3f9d92c6e993e399415ec1b8dfa8818","tid":1133344,"uid":120715,"like":250,"dislike":0,"score":250,"quote":{"